
'''''Zinabu'''''  ni filime yo muri [[Gana]] yo mu 1987 iyobowe na William Akuffo na Richard Quartey<ref>Zinabu, the first Ghanaian film to be shot using a video camera <nowiki>https://ghanaianmuseum.com</nowiki> › History</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Zinabu avuga amateka ''y'umupfumu winjiye mu bukristo''<ref>Ghanaian Video Tales | TIEFF - 民族誌影展 <nowiki>https://www.tieff.org</nowiki> › films › ghanaian-video-tales</ref>''.'' 

== Umusaruro ==
Filime yafashwe mu 1985 ikoresheje kamera ya videwo, aho kuba kamera ya firime <ref>Nollywood Confidential - jstor <nowiki>https://www.jstor.org</nowiki> › stable</ref>. Video yari igikoresho gishya muri kiriya gihe, ariko Akuffo yamenye ibyiza amashusho ya videwo yari afite kuri firime, kubera ko selile  yari ihenze kandi itanga imbogamizi zo kuyikwirakwiza<ref>Moving Pictures and Lived Experience - University of ... <nowiki>https://content.ucpress.edu</nowiki> › 13027.ch03.pdf</ref>. ''Zinabu'' yabaye firime ya mbere yo muri Gana yakozwe kuri videwo<ref>Ghanaian Video Tales | The NAFA Film Collection <nowiki>https://nafafilm.org</nowiki> › ...</ref>. 

== Ikwirakwizwa ==
Mu gihe cyo gutunganya ''Zinabu'', guverinoma ya [[Gana]] yashyizeho itegeko ribuza kureba amashusho, mu rwego rwo gukumira ingaruka mbi batekerezaga ko filime z’Abanyamerika n’Ubushinwa zitabifitiye uruhushya zigira ku muco wa [[Gana]]<ref>Of Witches and the Holy Spirit: Christian Film Production in ... <nowiki>https://marginalia.lareviewofbooks.org</nowiki> › witches-holy-s...</ref>. Iri tegeko ryakuweho mu 1987, ahanini bitewe nakazi ka Akuffo. Filime yakiriye bwa mbere muri Globe Cinema. Kwerekanwa byari bigamije kwigana firime isanzwe: umukinnyi wa videwo ntabwo yabonaga abari aho, kandi Akuffo yari mucyumba cyo kwerekana<ref>Ghallywood: An Evolution of Ghana's Film Industry - South ... <nowiki>https://www.sahistory.org.za</nowiki> › article › ghallywood-evo...</ref>. 

== Umurage ==
''Zinabu'' nicyo kintu cya mbere cyerekana amashusho yo muri [[Gana]], gitangira uburyo bushya bwo gutunganya amafilime kavukire yakura mu ntangiriro ya za 90. Mu 1988, hasohotse filime ebyiri za videwo, ariko iyi zigera kuri zirindwi mu 1991, zirenga 50 muri 1993.  Akuffo yakoze kandi ibisobanuro bitatu kuri ''Zinabu''<ref>Suɔmɔ Hi Fe Shika - Contemporary AndContemporary And <nowiki>https://contemporaryand.com</nowiki> › Events</ref> <ref>Remembering some classic Ghanaian movies - MyJoyOnline ... <nowiki>https://www.myjoyonline.com</nowiki> › throwback-thursday-re...</ref>. 
